no case pushed my friend

267
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:02,850
像《恐怖新娘》那样
to such mental and physical extremes

268
00:08:02,850 --> 00:08:06,350
挑战了我朋友的心理及生理极限
"as that of The Abominable Bride!"

269
00:08:07,050 --> 00:08:08,170
