It's got proper murders in it too.

1706
01:27:38,740 --> 01:27:39,910
你是这方面的专家嘛
You're the expert.

1707
01:27:39,920 --> 01:27:42,070
至于你的故事
As for your own tale,

1708
01:27:43,290 --> 01:27:46,820
你还确定你只用了7%的溶剂吗
are you sure it's still just a 7% solution that you take?

1709
01:27:46,820 --> 01:27:49,020
